snippet.title: Ranch Sim - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2020
snippet.description:
Rebuild your homestead into a prosperous ranch in the upcoming Ranch Sim. Releasing on PC Early Access in early 2021.

We’re going to be collecting YOUR video comments for our Summer of Gaming coverage. Head over to IGN and tell us what you’re most excited about, share predictions and reactions, as well as have conversations with other members! If you’re lucky, your video Yap may be played live, on-air! https://bit.ly/sog-yappa-video-commenting

Watch more Summer of Gaming here!
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLraFbwCoisJA6mVoDgLjCzra5jjG3V4SL

#ign #IGNSummerOfGaming
